Package: cce
Type: Package
Title: Counterfactual Comparator Engine for Survival Benchmarking
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Dai",
      family = "",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Author: Dai [aut, cre]
Description: Provides a reproducible toolkit for counterfactual comparator
    analyses in oncology-style survival settings. The package validates
    normalized trial-style inputs, builds analysis-ready cohorts, estimates
    standardized survival curves with g-formula and inverse probability of
    treatment weighting, projects assumption-based comparator curves for
    SOC-only scenarios, exports machine-readable outputs, and ships
    end-to-end tutorials for synthetic and public oncology data.
